{"tid":1098171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共擬花 2846 萬元辦支那國慶活動","createTime":"2019-04-09T01:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T21:23:55.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2615e771f76528ad08ef314ef061ec8d781c0016","tid":1098171,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:25:44.000Z","msg":"今年是支那國慶70周年。民政事務總署回覆立法會議員查詢時透露，今年籌辦慶祝支那的預算開支約為2,846萬元。署方亦表明，或需聘用額外的非公務員合約僱員協助籌辦部分活動。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/70-34_Qg3Nl_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F70-34_Qg3Nl_1200x0.png&h=66056ecb&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國慶70周年-港府擬花-2846-萬元辦慶祝活動/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B670%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E8%8A%B1-2846-%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%BE%A6%E6%85%B6%E7%A5%9D%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%2F&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLR6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=5fe035f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B670%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E8%8A%B1-2846-%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%BE%A6%E6%85%B6%E7%A5%9D%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%2F&h=00e2d9c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國慶70周年-港府擬花-2846-萬元辦慶祝活動/</a>"},{"pid":"da9a9508cdb0583977e31a452d129aa9abe31412","tid":1098171,"uid":33878,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:26:28.000Z","msg":"含撚啦"},{"pid":"7ceee4f49c1a25937743e5a7889204e508a06df8","tid":1098171,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:26:48.000Z","msg":"立法會財務委員會召開特別會議審議《財政預算案》，多位立法會議員都作出書面提問，要求政府交代今年支那國慶活動的預算開支。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署的書面回覆稱，署方今年將會舉辦或協辦的活動包括升旗儀式、國慶酒會、全港性嘉年華及展覽、文藝晚會。在地區活動方面，全港18區將懸掛彩旗布置城市景觀，18區民政事務處亦會舉辦慶祝活動。<br />\n<br />\n署方指，籌辦慶祝國慶70周年的活動，預算開支約為2,846萬元，當中約285萬元為宣傳開支。政府指，籌辦活動大部分工作將由民政總署的現有人員執行，當慶祝活動陸續展開，政府或需聘用額外的非公務員合約僱員協助籌辦部分活動，惟現時無法提供額外員工開支的確實資料。"},{"pid":"9b8d1a9fdb8963b2756085de489a77e300ca5209","tid":1098171,"uid":36143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:29:06.000Z","msg":"全港性嘉年華"},{"pid":"361d87894c52901d13f73cdb14a41713dd6fa062","tid":1098171,"uid":37661,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"加香港打工仔3,5,7日假，我就支持啦。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，國喪咋。<br />\n<br />\n冚家剷都拎嚟慶祝。"},{"pid":"1f6bc74c7044526ff0eb6ff97cee4a14d660a611","tid":1098171,"uid":37661,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，又搞到全香港旗海咁。<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦，無人想見到呀。"},{"pid":"31a594df6ab95c3d8c83ce7a6c6d9e9b2970b05a","tid":1098171,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"361d87894c52901d13f73cdb14a41713dd6fa062","tid":1098171,"uid":37661,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"加香港打工仔3,5,7日假，我就支持啦。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，國喪咋。<br />\n<br />\n冚家剷都拎嚟慶祝。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:33:31.000Z","msg":"國共內戰紀念日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實國共內戰停咗火未？有無簽和約？"},{"pid":"7baf26ba437373e4f68ff22331e8df6d8dcb4fb9","tid":1098171,"uid":1886,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jMnM81u.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMnM81u.gif&h=e246f3a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63598c3fea881b84ec1eff66426ec82bed281d8b","tid":1098171,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>升旗儀式、國慶酒會</strong>、全港性嘉年華及展覽、<strong>文藝晚會</strong>。在地區活動方面，全港18區將懸掛彩旗布置城市景觀，18區民政事務處亦會舉辦慶祝活動<br />\n<br />\n普通巿民係咪無得參加"},{"pid":"01ef4afbc3866